    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我注意到您提到了几个基础设施组件——负载均衡器、WorkerNode、RedisCache、IngressController，还有EtcdCluster。这些是要作为状态机的外部事件源和守卫条件吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
