      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，EtcdCluster是最终持久化存储。WorkerNode负责检测目录页和章节计数，RedisCache缓存前端信号，IngressController处理标题和Back Matter的信号检测。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主干状态：从负载均衡器到Init，再到Front Matter。Front Matter之后应该能转到TOC或者Body吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Init",
        "Front",
        "TOC",
        "Body"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的。关键在事件驱动：E_toc表示检测到目录页信号，这时候从Front Matter进入TOC状态。E_heading是标题信号，或者既没有E_toc也没有E_front时，直接进入Body。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Front",
        "TOC",
        "Body",
        "E_toc",
        "E_heading",
        "E_front"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "那如果Front Matter里持续有E_front信号，但既没有标题也没有目录呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Front",
        "E_front",
        "E_heading",
        "E_toc"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "这种情况Front Matter要自循环，保持在前置状态直到出现明确转移信号。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Front"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了Front的自循环。现在TOC这块，我加了G_toc_detected守卫——检测到目录页或连续目录持续时保持，否则遇到E_heading或守卫不成立就进Body。",
      "elements_involved": [
