      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，但Body的自循环条件我需要修正一下。应该是当EtcdCluster条件不满足时保持，而不是直接写否定。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Body",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我调整Body的自循环条件，改为\"非Infra_EtcdCluster\"的守卫形式。另外Body到Back Matter的转移是E_back信号且WorkerNode的章节计数满足条件？",
